---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About">
  <section class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr]">
    <div>
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">
        About
      </p>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-5xl">
       Building real systems, not just projects.
      </h1>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
    <p>
       I build and learn through real projects — focusing on functional applications rather than theory alone.
    </p>

     <p>
       My approach is straightforward: understand how things actually work by building them. 
       From frontend interfaces to backend logic, I focus on clarity, structure, and practical use.
     </p>

      <p>
       Alongside development, I work with the systems behind the applications — including server setup, 
       networking fundamentals, and virtualization. This gives me a broader understanding of how software runs in real environments.
      </p>

       <p>
        I’m currently focused on improving my understanding of modern web technologies, clean architecture, 
        and building projects that reflect real-world use cases.
      </p>
      </div>
    </div>

       <div class="mt-10">
       <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
         Infrastructure & Networking
       </h2>

      <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
         I work with the underlying systems that support applications, including basic network setup, 
         structured cabling, and server configuration.
      </p>
      </div> 


      <div class="mt-8">
       <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
         Systems Administration
       </h2>

      <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
         I manage and experiment with different system environments, focusing on stability and control.
       </p>

  <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-slate-700">
    <li>Windows Server environments</li>
    <li>Linux systems</li>
    <li>Virtualization (Proxmox, ESXi)</li>
  </ul>
</div>

    <aside class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-550">
        Snapshot
      </p>

      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-slate-700">
        <li>Building through real-world projects</li>
        <li>Working across development and infrastructure</li>
        <li>Hands-on with systems administration and virtualization</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </section>
</MainLayout>